						<div class="postbody">Is there a list on the internet where people rate the difficulty of each NES game? I.e. a list where &quot;Contra&quot; is rated as quite difficult, but fair, &quot;Ninja Gaiden&quot; as frustratingly and unfairly difficult and &quot;Kirby's Adventure&quot; as easy.<br />(Preferrably with a filter option.)</div>

					
